{"id": "1311276058166693929", "channel_id": "1311276058166693929", "type": 0, "author_id": "1065139474268422189", "author_name": "jiangmengsheng", "author_bot": false, "content": "塔薇的通晓万物之理被啼鸣后变为三费，然后其他卡也被变为三费，然后就变成加法了，直接六费，可啼鸣的技能描述为将消费变为三费，这应该是bug吧，之前还有变成八费，不知道怎么算的。", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T10:22:54.598000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1311276059328778272", "filename": "2024-11-27_181506.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2738002, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1311276058166693929/1311276059328778272/2024-11-27_181506.png?ex=6a005c7e&is=69ff0afe&hm=b5caae05ebd5af9fc09d6e6b5ad051fb326e542ee42f64ba3777a846310f0cb9&"}, {"id": "1311276060066713630", "filename": "2024-11-27_181837.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 638449, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1311276058166693929/1311276060066713630/2024-11-27_181837.png?ex=6a005c7f&is=69ff0aff&hm=878577d7f38213f95f74ea9c403edc804c20464fe50be038ae5d4a0aedb6c30d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1311276058166693929", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "塔薇的通晓万物之理", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1311306435568603148", "channel_id": "1311306435568603148", "type": 0, "author_id": "1301603791254323220", "author_name": "awecat0961", "author_bot": false, "content": "半周年不仅送了限定自选，还有+十二金命轮\n一周年就送了一个塔威，还要登录七天,毫无诚意\n半周年的时候可没有加四超限之类的，换而言之就是现在一个限定的价值被大大压缩了，塔威三启和超限之间差距可不是一般的大,猫还说\n这游戏活不下去了，不会逼氪，新角色免费送，我还以为送的是加12的东西，结果就这。\n出的活动也是，打的一点都不爽，你们不会认为有玩家认为容灾好玩儿吧，削弱角色和膨胀敌人哪个能给玩家正面感受，你们应该自己清楚。", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T12:23:37.135000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1311306435568603148", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你们这一周年福利怎么比半周年少好多", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
